---
title: Double Korean-Style Prawns & Charred Corn Slaw with Sriracha Mayo
description: If you’re having sticky glazed prawns then you will need a handy-dandy slaw to go with them. A charred corn slaw, drizzled in a punchy sriracha mayo and tossed through with veggies and spring onion is the perfect slaw for the job. It’s a winning combination!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/664ed2090ab4934df86335af-a2f175de.jpeg
